      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん。ごめんなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry. I’m so sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "全く、危ないところでしたわ。これは一度焼き肉でも\nおごってもらわないといけませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My goodness! That was a close call. You’ll have to treat us to\nKorean BBQ to atone for that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.150000023841857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.68333335717519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今までずっと私達を引っ張ってくれたのは\n琴乃ちゃんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But don’t forget‚ the one who’s been pulling the group’s weight all this time\nis Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.35000002384186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ\nこれで少しだけお返しが出来たかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right!\nI think that’s the least we could do for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.12145121097565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 20.321451210929087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "へ？\nい、いや……私だって感謝はしていますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha?\nD-don’t misunderstand me. I’m grateful as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 25.25478454426241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "失敗やミスは誰にでもある。だから、みんなで\nカバーし合って前に進む。それがグループだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone makes mistakes. So it’s up to the rest of us\nto cover for someone when they do. That’s what a group does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.87821980312781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "渚……みんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa… girls…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.00165506199317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.00165506199321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "では、出場グループは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would all the groups here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.79646225765663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "全員ステージに集まって下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "please make their way to the stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2098975975843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
