      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 57.29055825425397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-host003.m4a",
      "text": "僅差でしたが、セミファイナルに進む二組目は\n…………月のテンペスト！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a close one‚ but the group advancing to the semi-finals is…\nMoon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.02389158758735,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4723.891587587382,
          "startTime": 62.02389158758738
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "…………良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a relief…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 67.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……良かったよぉぉ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ what a relief. I’m so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 70.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "泣いている場合ではありませんわよ\n次はいよいよ、LizNoirと当たるのですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now’s no time for tears.\nWe have to face off against LizNoir next.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。サニピはトリエル、私達はリズノワ\n……バンプロダクションの二大看板と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Sunny Peace versus TRINITYAiLE. Us versus LizNoir.\nWe’re up against the poster girls of Van Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 85.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "うん\n…………えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nHuh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong‚ Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 90.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……なんか……\n視線を感じたような気がして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It just felt like…\n…someone was staring at me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 94.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 94.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_02-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "……行くぞ。一応挨拶しに行くのが筋だろう\nバンプロは、この業界では最大手の事務所の一つだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s go. We have to go introduce ourselves—it’s only proper.\nVan Productions is one of the biggest agencies in this biz.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
